sources.description:
Shango is a Texas Ranger who finds himself up against a former Confederate officer and his gang of thugs who have been terrorizing a local border town in search of gold.

This video is available with dubbed Audio in English, German & Italian. And also subtitled in more than 30 languages. Click on ⚙️ and choose subtitles and/or audio tracks.

Original title: Shango, la pistola infallibile (1970)
Director: Edoardo Mulargia
Writers: Edoardo Mulargia, Anthony Steffen
Stars: Anthony Steffen, Eduardo Fajardo, Maurice Poli
Genres: Action, Drama, Western
